content.rendered:
Directed by Rajeev Chaudhari.

Written by Vibhanshu Vaibhav.

Cast Sunny Leone(Sunaina). Rajneesh Duggal(Raj Malhotra (as Rajniesh Duggall)). Daniel Weber(Daniel Peterson). Rajeev Verma(KK Malhotra) . Akshita Agnihotri(Natasha). Arushi Ahluwalia(Pramila). Sahil Arora(Harry). Usha Bachani(Janki Verma). Rina Charaniya(Andrea). Prveshika Chauhan(Deepa). Manoj Dutt(Doctor). Pratik Garg(Jojo). Gary(Canadian Businessman). Avtar Gill(Amarnath Kapoor). Jaswinder Kaur(Leena). Dilip Mehra(Rajan Saxena). Gaelyn Mendonca(Anchor). Muthukutty Nadar(Sunaina Secretary #3). Ziesha Nancy(Sanjana). Paras(Rob). Arjun Paswan(Friend). Raviraj(Security Guard). Nirmal Sandhu(Sunaina Secretary #1). Shambhu(Bhola). Sanjiv Shrivasthav(Sunaina Secretary #2). Richa Pradhan Singh(Maayra). Yuvraj S Singh(Monish (as Yuvraj Singh)).Sanjeev Srivastava. Parth Suri(Monty). Neha Thakur(Dolly). Sagar Tirlotkar(Panzy Guy). Vibhanshu Vaibhav(Dixit). Rajiv Verma(K.K Malhotra). Rajsi Verma(Shobha). Isha Vyas(Sunaina’s Maid). Ramna Wadhawan(Daadiji). Anuja Walie(Receptionist at K.K Office)

Languages Hindi. English.

Producers Prince Adhikari. Rajeev Chaudhari. Roshni Chaudhari. Arjun Kudva. Vijay Vaibhani. Vijay Valbhani.

Production Avanti Films. Crystal Movies.
